{"tid":2084634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"三個紀律部隊組織：將全力協助打擊黑暴 斬斷外部勢力黑手","createTime":"2020-06-29T11:04:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T12:57:47.000Z","uid":7542,"like":5,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fabf296644a37f87ab7edd15740945ee4b7a0d7e","tid":2084634,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:04:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">紀律部隊</span>最有紀律係今次 </strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n三個紀律部隊員方組織發表聲明，表示全力支持全國人大常委會通過港區國安法。聲明由香港海關人員總會、香港入境事務處人員協會及香港懲教署懲教助理總會聯合發出，表示作為<strong>愛國愛港紀律部隊工會及公務員隊伍一分子</strong>，將<strong>全力配合全國人大常委會通過有關立法，履行維護國家安全的職責</strong>，呼籲會員必須清楚認識自己公務員的身分和職責，既要效忠香港特區政府，亦必須效忠國家，責無旁貸維護國家主權、安全和發展利益等各項工作。<br />\n<br />\n聲明形容，<strong>港區國安法是以「有效的法律措施打擊黑暴，斬斷外部勢力干預香港的黑手」</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534744-20200629.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534744-20200629.htm&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=61ffced4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534744-20200629.htm&h=2707f763\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534744-20200629.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1e14d1f153f1c807433061fa6ce53b8209118238","tid":2084634,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi7ZF_dgqG3s&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=c92c0736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i7ZF_dgqG3s</a> <br />\n<br />\n剪片時聽了超過十次，但每次都起哂雞皮，去到最後都係忍唔住喊。<br />\n<br />\n如果你開始恐懼、退縮、氣餒 &mdash; 閉起雙眼，由頭聽到尾。提醒自己，你不是孤單的；亦不要讓其他抗爭者感到孤單。"},{"pid":"67fec3f459e2ae1ca8dbbb70dad0bfc4e2243c57","tid":2084634,"uid":57671,"like":0,"disli